          "target_tier": "t3",
          "dwell_ms": 3800,
          "copy": "If the judge and T2.5 disagree about what the right answer is, the panel debates. Three different models, eight seconds budget, real consensus. Only runs when the cheaper tiers couldn't reach agreement."
